# CLAUDE.md

This repository uses the Harness workflow for Claude Code.

## Read First

1. Read `docs/memory/constitution.md`
2. Read `docs/context/experience/index.md`
3. Read `docs/context/rules/risk-rules.md`
4. Load only matching experience files
5. Read `docs/context/rules/agent-workflow.md`
6. Read `docs/context/project/project-overview.md` and `docs/context/team/development-standards.md` as needed
7. When a path fails or a correction appears, update the current change `session-memory.md`
8. Before finishing, decide whether to promote reusable lessons into `docs/context/experience/`
